metadata.name: Contrast of Time
metadata.description:
The black and white street photo portrays a woman standing on Saint-Malo's ancient medieval stairways, capturing the city's timeless quality that reflects its rich history and charm. The woman's modern appearance contrasts with the old architecture, creating a sense of connection between the past and present. The interplay of light and shadows creates depth and dimension to the scene, inviting viewers to appreciate the beauty of this historic city.
Photographer: Masis Usenmez
Bio: EFIAP honored, award-winning Armenian origin Turkish street and documentary photographer based in France.
Edition: 1/1
